# Test commands (agents)

On Windows, `vendor\bin\phpunit` has no `.exe` extension. Invoking it directly opens a "choose app" dialog instead of running tests.

**Never** use `vendor/bin/phpunit` or `vendor\bin\phpunit` in shell commands.

**Never** run `docker compose … run composer vue:check` — the `composer` image has no npm. Use `.\scripts\vue-check.ps1` or the `vue` service via scripts.

**Prefer** `.\scripts\*.ps1` or `.\scripts\mrt.ps1` over raw `docker compose` — wrappers use `--no-deps`, conditional `npm ci`, tools-shell exec, and single-container check/lint. See `docs/DOCKER_SCRIPTS_PLAN.md`.

**Timings:** add `-Timings` to gate scripts, or set `$env:MRT_SCRIPT_TIMINGS=1` / `export MRT_SCRIPT_TIMINGS=1` (bash: `--timings`). Logs `[timing] step — Ns` per major step.

## Docker dev reset

| Context | Command |
|---------|---------|
| Full reset (Windows) | `.\scripts\docker-dev-reset.ps1` |
| Full reset (Linux/WSL) | `./scripts/docker-dev-reset.sh` |
| Rebuild WordPress image | `-Build` / `--build` on the reset script above |
| Stack already up | `-SkipCompose` / `--skip-compose` |
| Plugin sync (slow Windows bind mount) | `.\scripts\docker-watch.ps1` or `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 dev watch` |

## Unified CLI

| Context | Command |
|---------|---------|
| Help | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 help` |
| Same as check.ps1 | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 check` |
| Same as test.ps1 | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 test` |
| Dev reset | `.\scripts\mrt.ps1 dev reset` |

## PHP

| Context | Command |
|---------|---------|
| Full PHP gate (Windows) | `.\scripts\check.ps1` — validate + PHPStan + PHPUnit + PHPCS in Docker (one container) |
| PHP + Vue gate | `.\scripts\check.ps1 -Vue` |
| PHPUnit only (Windows) | `.\scripts\test.ps1` — Docker by default |
| Single test file | `.\scripts\test.ps1 tests/Unit/SomeTest.php` |
| Host PHP 8.2+ (optional) | `.\scripts\test.ps1 -Local` |
| PHPStan + PHPCS only | `.\scripts\lint.ps1` |
| PHP coverage (exploratory) | `.\scripts\coverage.ps1` — PCOV in Docker; see `docs/TEST_COVERAGE.md` |

## Vue

| Context | Command |
|---------|---------|
| Full Vue gate (Windows) | `.\scripts\vue-check.ps1` — typecheck + Vitest + build + verify in Docker |
| Full Vue gate (Linux/WSL) | `bash scripts/vue-check.sh` |
| Host Node (optional) | `.\scripts\vue-check.ps1 -Local` or `bash scripts/vue-check.sh --local` |

`scripts/test.ps1`, `scripts/check.ps1`, and `scripts/vue-check.ps1` use Docker by default. Same codebase via volume mount.

See `docs/PHP_INSTALL_WINDOWS.md`, `docs/DEVELOPER.md`, and `docs/DOCKER_SCRIPTS_PLAN.md` for humans.
